net.rptools.maptool.model.MacroButtonPro.label: dnd5e_RollExpression_DnDBeyondAttack
net.rptools.maptool.model.MacroButtonPro.toolTip:
Creates a DnDBeyond Attack RollExpression with an optional provided name.
There is no roll for a DnDBeyond Attack. just the selected attack that it applies

arg(0) = optional name of the DnDBeyond generated attack

A roll expression that can be used to indicate this expression came from generated attacks
